author: marta.paulina
text:
Remember, you can have a couple of lean years and then bounce right back. 
Trust your ability to rejuvenate yourself.

author: marta.paulina
text:
Never regret the love you’ve given. 
If they can’t love you back— it’s ok.
People don’t owe you shit.

author: marta.paulina
text:
Quitting feels great. 
Sometimes you just gotta stop right away. 
So quit that job. 
Ghost that person. 
Say ‘Goodbye”.

author: marta.paulina
text:
Beware of a woman who’s chill with her craziness—
She will drive you crazy.

author: marta.paulina
text: Today I had a realization— I’m crazy. And I’m so cool about it.

text: I need a Virgo woman or man in my life.

text:
Hey, I’m leaving. 
But I’ll come back in Dior.

text: Me to me when I go on my morning solitary walk: make sure you look like a total bitch so nobody dares to approach you.

author: marta.paulina
text: I can’t wait for people to find out I’m really a bitch—

author: marta.paulina
text:
From now on, 
I only bend over backwards for myself only.

author: marta.paulina
text: My idea of fun includes drinking a Capri Sun at 10 pm so I can stay up all night.

author: marta.paulina
text: Don’t yell at your kid bc you’re mad at your boss.

author: marta.paulina
text: I know I’m not everyone’s cup of tea — and I love that about me.

author: marta.paulina
text: It’s so hard to find people who are not obsessed with money— everything’s about making money, or consuming and I’m so tired of that energy.

author: marta.paulina
text:
I am making a conscious effort to make more room for romance in my life—
It’s been too long since I let a man treat me right.

author: marta.paulina
text: Am I delusional? Yes, and proud of it.

author: marta.paulina
text:
Honestly most movie plots are so stupid— especially lately. 
It’s been a while since I’ve watched a movie where actors had good chemistry together.

author: marta.paulina
text: I need some seduction in my life! 🙏

author: marta.paulina
text: Wow, all of this inner work and you’re still a bitch…

author: marta.paulina
text:
I’m realizing everyone’s so fake around me— 
and I’m the fakest of them all trying to fit into places I outgrew long time ago.

text: I’m “I go alone to functions” level of badass.

text:
Just had a major realization— wow, several actually. 
This eclipse was crazy.

text: Don’t fuck around with me, build with me.

text:
I often think about how we willingly show total strangers on social media our most intimate moments— we willingly give up parts of ourselves . 
Cause that’s freedom ?
